  "original_title": "\u0dad\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0dab\u0dba\u0dcf\u0da7 \u0db4\u0dc4\u0dbb \u0daf\u0dd4\u0db1\u0dca \u0dba\u0dd4\u0daf \u0dc4\u0db8\u0dd4\u0daf\u0dcf \u0db1\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0db0\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0da7 \u0dc0\u0dd0\u0da9 \u0dc0\u0dbb\u0daf\u0dd3",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The army officer who assaulted the youth was dismissed",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The army officer who has been accused of assaulting a person at Yaggahapitiya gas station in Kurunegala has been temporarily removed from duty with immediate effect, the army says.",
        "A senior officer of the Army said that the removal from those duties will be effective until the investigation carried out by the Army regarding the incident is completed."
      ],
